title: A Look at the Upcoming Supreme Court Term
itunes:title: A Look at the Upcoming Supreme Court Term
description:
Former United States Solicitor General Gregory Garre, a partner at Latham & Watkins, discusses the upcoming term of the Supreme Court and whether it will be as controversial as the last term.

June Grasso hosts.
